DateTime::Locale::ks_IN(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::ks_IN(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::ks_IN - Locale data examples for the Kashmiri India (ks-IN) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Kashmiri India locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = بۆموار, فرؤری 5, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = جُمہ, دسمبر 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = بٹوار, ستمبر 15, -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = فرؤری 5, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = دسمبر 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = ستمبر 15, -10
